          <ul class="text-blue-800 space-y-2 text-sm">
            <li>• 6 completely free AI chatbots that rival premium services</li>
            <li>• Real-world testing results and performance comparisons</li>
            <li>• Step-by-step setup guides for each platform</li>
            <li>• Pro tips to maximize your free AI experience</li>
          </ul>
