            alt="Person using multiple AI chatbots on laptop screen showing various free AI interfaces"
            class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-2xl"
            loading="eager"
          />
          <figcaption class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-3 italic">
            Free AI chatbots have revolutionized access to artificial intelligence in 2025
          </figcaption>
        </figure>
      </div>

