              <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Perplexity AI stands out by providing sources and citations for its responses. It's like having a research assistant that not only gives you answers but shows you where the information comes from.</p>
              
              <div class="bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
